Class BSTrun

  • java.lang.Object
    • BSTrun

  • public class BSTrun
extends java.lang.Object
    The num Arraylist stores the number of counts when finding each Dam The BinarySearchTree temp stores the Dam objects the maxarr array stores the worst case value when finding the object The minarr array stores the best case value when finding the object The insert array stores the number of comparisons when inserting the Dam object

        public static void main(java.lang.String[] args)
        The main method is used to add the elements in the BinarySearchTree The number of insert comparisons made when adding each element is stored After each addition, every element in the BinarySearchTree is searched and the find comparisons is stored At the end of the program, the best/worse/average case for the insert and find operations is printed out
